### ========================================
### 智慧云脑诊疗平台 - API测试集合
### 使用说明：
###   1. 数据库已包含基础数据（患者、医生、挂号记录等）
###   2. 先执行"登录"请求，获取token
###   3. token会自动保存，无需手动粘贴
###   4. 按顺序从上到下执行请求
### ========================================

### ---- 环境变量 ----
@outpatient = http://localhost:8092
@drugstore = http://localhost:8092
@ai = http://localhost:8092
@token =
@newRegisterId =

### ========================================
### 1. 健康检查
### ========================================

### 1-1. 健康检查 - 门诊模块
GET {{outpatient}}/outpatient/actuator/health

### 1-2. 健康检查 - 药库模块
GET {{drugstore}}/drugstore/actuator/health

### 1-3. 健康检查 - AI模块
GET {{ai}}/ai/actuator/health

### ========================================
### 2. 查询可挂号医生
### 注意：数据库中有 scheduling 表，日期为 2026-05-23
### ========================================

GET {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/patient/doctors?deptId=1&visitDate=2026-05-23&noon=上午&pageNum=1&pageSize=10

### ========================================
### 3. 登录
### ========================================

### 3-1. 登录 - 医生登录成功（使用 realname 匹配数据库）
# @name login
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "张建国",
  "password": "123456",
  "loginType": "DOCTOR"
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 200 && response.body.code === 200) {
        client.global.set("token", response.body.data.token);
        client.log("Token已保存");
    }
%}

### 3-2. 登录 - 密码错误
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "张建国",
  "password": "wrongpassword",
  "loginType": "DOCTOR"
}

### ========================================
### 4. 挂号 - 新增挂号
### ========================================

### 4-1. 挂号 - 正常挂号（使用数据库 patient 表字段）
# @name register
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/patient/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "caseNumber": "HN202600001",
  "realName": "张三",
  "gender": "男",
  "cardNumber": "11010119900307663X",
  "birthdate": "1990-03-07",
  "phone": "13912345678",
  "homeAddress": "北京市朝阳区XX路1号",
  "deptId": 1,
  "doctorId": 1,
  "visitDate": "2026-05-23",
  "noon": "上午",
  "registLevelId": 1,
  "settleCategoryId": 2,
  "registMethod": "微信"
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 200 && response.body.code === 200) {
        client.global.set("newRegisterId", response.body.data);
        client.log("新挂号ID已保存: " + response.body.data);
    }
%}

### 4-2. 挂号 - 姓名为空（参数校验）
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/patient/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "realName": "",
  "gender": "男",
  "cardNumber": "11010119900307663X",
  "birthdate": "1990-03-07",
  "homeAddress": "北京市",
  "deptId": 1,
  "doctorId": 1,
  "visitDate": "2026-05-23",
  "noon": "上午",
  "registLevelId": 1,
  "settleCategoryId": 2
}

### 4-3. 挂号 - 身份证号格式错误
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/patient/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "realName": "张三",
  "gender": "男",
  "cardNumber": "123456",
  "birthdate": "1990-03-07",
  "homeAddress": "北京市",
  "deptId": 1,
  "doctorId": 1,
  "visitDate": "2026-05-23",
  "noon": "上午",
  "registLevelId": 1,
  "settleCategoryId": 2
}

### ========================================
### 5. 病历列表 - 使用已存在的患者ID=1
### ========================================

GET {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/patient/records?patientId=1&pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### 6. 病历详情 - 使用已存在的挂号ID=1
### ========================================

GET {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/patient/records/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### 7. 医生待诊列表 - 医生ID=1（张建国）
### ========================================

GET {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/doctor/patients?doctorId=1&visitState=REGISTERED&pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### 8. 保存病历 - 使用已存在的挂号ID=1
### ========================================

### 8-1. 保存病历 - 正常保存（匹配 medical_record 表字段）
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/doctor/medical-record
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "registerId": 6,
  "readme": "头痛头晕3天",
  "present": "患者3天前无明显诱因出现头痛、头晕，呈阵发性",
  "presentTreat": "未治疗",
  "history": "高血压病史5年",
  "allergy": "无",
  "physique": "BP 140/90mmHg，神清",
  "proposal": "头颅CT检查",
  "careful": "避免劳累",
  "diagnosis": "高血压病"
}

### 8-2. 保存病历 - registerId不存在
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/doctor/medical-record
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "registerId": 99999,
  "readme": "测试",
  "present": "测试",
  "history": "无",
  "allergy": "无",
  "physique": "正常",
  "proposal": "无",
  "careful": "无",
  "diagnosis": "测试"
}

### ========================================
### 9. AI诊断建议 - 使用已存在的病历ID=1
### ========================================

POST {{ai}}/ai/api/ai/diagnosis/suggest
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "medicalRecordId": 1,
  "symptoms": "头痛头晕",
  "history": "高血压",
  "physique": "BP140/90"
}

### ========================================
### 10. 开检查申请 - 使用已存在的挂号ID=1
### ========================================

### 10-1. 开检查 - 正常开立（匹配 check_request 表字段）
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/doctor/check-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "registerId": 6,
  "items": [
    {
      "medicalTechnologyId": 1,
      "checkInfo": "头颅CT平扫",
      "checkPosition": "头部"
    }
  ]
}

### 10-2. 开检查 - 未接诊患者
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/doctor/check-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "registerId": 99999,
  "items": [
    {
      "medicalTechnologyId": 1,
      "checkInfo": "测试",
      "checkPosition": "头部"
    }
  ]
}

### ========================================
### 11. AI影像上传 - 使用存在的checkRequestId=1
### ========================================

POST {{ai}}/api/ai/image/upload?checkRequestId=1&registerId=6
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample_head_ct.nii.gz"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ./test-files/sample_head_ct.nii.gz
--WebAppBoundary--

### ========================================
### 12. AI影像分析
### ========================================

POST {{ai}}/api/ai/image/analyze
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "imageFileId": 1,
  "checkRequestId": 1
}

### ========================================
### 13. AI生成报告
### ========================================

POST {{ai}}/api/ai/report/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "checkRequestId": 1,
  "reportType": "CHECK",
  "rawData": "CT影像原始数据"
}

