### ========================================
### 16. 开处方
### ========================================

### 16-1. 开处方 - 正常开立（匹配 prescription 和 prescription_detail 表）
# @name prescription
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/doctor/prescription
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "registerId": 6,
  "doctorId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "drugId": 1,
      "usageRoute": "口服",
      "frequency": "每日一次",
      "dosage": "100mg",
      "singleDose": "1片",
      "useDays": 30,
      "drugNumber": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 16-2. 开处方 - 药品数量超库存
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/doctor/prescription
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "registerId": 6,
  "doctorId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "drugId": 1,
      "usageRoute": "口服",
      "frequency": "每日一次",
      "dosage": "100mg",
      "singleDose": "1片",
      "useDays": 7,
      "drugNumber": 9999
    }
  ]
}

### ========================================
### 17. 门诊确诊
### ========================================

PUT {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/doctor/diagnosis/confirm
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "registerId": 6,
  "diagnosis": "高血压病",
  "cure": "口服降压药，定期监测血压",
  "diseaseIds": [2]
}

### ========================================
### 18. 查看检查结果
### ========================================

GET {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/doctor/check-results/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### 19. 收费
### ========================================

### 19-1. 收费 - 正常收费
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/admin/finance/charge
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "registerId": 6,
  "itemIds": [1],
  "chargeMethod": "微信",
  "amount": 70.50
}

### 19-2. 收费 - 金额不匹配
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/admin/finance/charge
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "registerId": 1,
  "itemIds": [1],
  "chargeMethod": "微信",
  "amount": 1.00
}

