### 29. 退号
### ========================================
POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/patient/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "realName": "李四",
  "gender": "女",
  "cardNumber": "110101198505121234",
  "birthdate": "1985-05-12",
  "homeAddress": "上海市浦东新区XX路2号",
  "phone": "13987654321",
  "deptId": 1,
  "doctorId": 1,
  "visitDate": "2026-05-23",
  "noon": "上午",
  "registLevelId": 1,
  "settleCategoryId": 1,
  "registMethod": "微信"
}
### 29-1. 退号 - 正常退号（使用新创建的挂号）
PUT {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/patient/register/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "registerId": 7,
  "cancelReason": "临时有事"
}

### 29-2. 退号 - 已开检查不可退（使用已开检查的挂号ID=1）
PUT {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/patient/register/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "registerId": 1,
  "cancelReason": "测试"
}

### ========================================
### 30. 退出登录
### ========================================

POST {{outpatient}}/outpatient/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
